WEBVTT

00:00:29.526 --> 00:00:31.667
and so, as you can imagine,

00:00:31.691 --> 00:00:34.618
African-American culture
is kind of serious around my home.

00:00:34.642 --> 00:00:38.888
So I was very proud that my son
was excited about what he had learned

00:00:38.912 --> 00:00:40.063
that day in school.

00:00:40.087 --> 00:00:42.027
So I said, "What did you learn?"

00:00:42.051 --> 00:00:45.529
He said, "I learned about Rosa Parks."

00:00:45.907 --> 00:00:48.959
I said, "OK, what did you learn
about Rosa Parks?"

00:00:48.983 --> 00:00:54.497
He said, "I learned that Rosa Parks
was this frail, old black woman

00:00:54.521 --> 00:00:56.371
in the 1950s

00:00:56.395 --> 00:00:58.829
in Montgomery, Alabama.

00:00:58.853 --> 00:01:01.103
And she sat down on this bus,